00:44:57.212 --> 00:45:00.332
when you add IL6. But we don't see any changes actually in any of the

762
00:45:00.392 --> 00:45:01.641
anti-apoptotic proteins

763
00:45:02.552 --> 00:45:06.222
when we looked at this. And then what Vikas did was he actually took cells.

764
00:45:06.252 --> 00:45:09.012
He only treated them for three hours with both

765
00:45:09.112 --> 00:45:12.552
ABT-737 and IL6. So he didn't really give a chance

