00:46:47.051 --> 00:46:50.792
he only saw at serine 69, where we had an antibody,

793
00:46:51.171 --> 00:46:54.812
this phosphorylation constitutive, and this has a BRAF-activating

794
00:46:54.852 --> 00:46:58.152
mutation, which would be consistent with, again, MEK-driven

795
00:46:58.492 --> 00:46:58.952
events.

796
00:47:00.872 --> 00:47:04.192
But he looked in cell lines, and he used a phospho affinity gel

