00:47:38.792 --> 00:47:42.752
phosphorylated here. And then we used a second data set that I'm

808
00:47:42.772 --> 00:47:45.632
not showing here from Arun Weida at UCSF and found the same things.

809
00:47:46.172 --> 00:47:50.092
Moreover, recently Jan Cronke had published a paper doing

