00:50:12.408 --> 00:50:15.928
ex vivo treatment for 24 hours, where about half of our

853
00:50:15.968 --> 00:50:19.158
11;14s were below this 100 nanomolar IC50,

854
00:50:19.968 --> 00:50:23.228
where only about 10% of the non-11;14 samples were.

855
00:50:23.368 --> 00:50:25.228
So we wanted to understand this a little bit more.

856
00:50:25.268 --> 00:50:25.628
And so what

857
00:50:26.648 --> 00:50:30.448
Vikas did was he actually took 31 cell lines and

858
00:50:30.528 --> 00:50:32.748
treated them with venetoclax, generated dose curves.

859
00:50:32.768 --> 00:50:36.128
And sure enough, just like the patient samples and just like the patients, about

860
00:50:36.168 --> 00:50:38.208
half of the 11;14s were sensitive,

861
00:50:39.268 --> 00:50:42.248
where only 10% of the non-11;14s were.

862
00:50:42.688 --> 00:50:46.408
And you could see differences in RNA-seq in BCL2 expression

863
00:50:46.448 --> 00:50:50.228
and MCL1. And you can look at these

