00:57:15.524 --> 00:57:17.024
to test it the treatment?

978
00:57:18.644 --> 00:57:19.424
Yeah, that's first.

979
00:57:19.624 --> 00:57:21.383
Okay, first one. So, first one, no.

980
00:57:21.464 --> 00:57:21.564
So

981
00:57:22.424 --> 00:57:22.624
clearly,

982
00:57:23.444 --> 00:57:26.444
in I think everything we ever tested, and we did it in patient samples too.

983
00:57:26.464 --> 00:57:29.984
When you combine a BCL2 inhibitor and an Mcl1 inhibitor, it's lights out.

