1003
00:58:34.664 --> 00:58:38.264
develop this conditional, the release this drug, just

1004
00:58:38.304 --> 00:58:41.324
avoiding to this heart disease toxicity?

1005
00:58:41.404 --> 00:58:45.344
Yeah. So to avoid the heart-- So could you target the Mcl1

