00:58:45.384 --> 00:58:45.904
inhibitor

1007
00:58:47.004 --> 00:58:50.284
to the tumor cells? It's an interesting idea.

1008
00:58:50.304 --> 00:58:53.424
The question would be, can you get enough into the tumors that way?

